## Visual Studio / .NET Core common ignores

# User-specific files
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Build results (apply to all subdirectories)
**/[Bb]in/
**/[Oo]bj/
**/out/

# Visual Studio Code
**/.vscode/

# Visual Studio cache/options
**/.vs/

# Rider
**/.idea/

# NuGet
**/packages/
**/*.nupkg
**/.nuget/

# Publish
**/PublishProfiles/
**/publish/

# IIS
**/IISExpress/*

# Logs
**/*.log
**/logs/

# Test results
**/TestResults/

# Resharper
_ReSharper*/
*.DotSettings.user

# Coverage
**/coverage/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Docker
docker-compose.override.yml

# Ignore uploaded files (user content)
src/SiteDiary.Web/uploads/

# User secrets (uncomment if you store secrets locally)
#secrets.json
